Ann Doran https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ann_Doran 0 Ann Lee Doran (July 28, 1911 – September 19, 2000) was an American character actress, possibly best known as the mother of Jim Stark (James Dean) in Rebel Without a Cause (1955). She was an early member of the Screen Actors Guild and served on the board of the Motion Picture Television Fund for 30 years.
